The paper discusses the security and privacy issues in the infrastructure and architecture of IoT, which falls under the category of "Computer Security and Cryptography" (cs.CR). It also talks about the connectivity and communication aspects of IoT, which is related to "Networking and Internet Architecture" (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the software engineering and development aspects of IoT, which is related to "Software Engineering" (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper talks about the system-level design and control of IoT, which is related to "Systems and Control" (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the privacy concerns related to IoT, which is related to "Computers and Society" (cs.CY).
